title: The Last Time (Taylor's Version) ft. Gary Lightbody
description:
This is such a beautiful song, and there are some insane theories behind it! Did she write this song because of a late pizza delivery? NO... but it is funny to talk about! And would you join us for Tayloroke?
Let us know what you think and what you want from us! There are lots of ways to reach us!
